      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "获得相对标准误差（Relative Standard Error，RSE）\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\mathrm{RSE}=\\frac{Standard Error}{Estimate}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Standard Error为样本的标准误，Estimate为样本的均值"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "nteract": {
          "transient": {
            "deleting": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "summary(lm.fit)$sigma "
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {

      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# 加入解释变量的非线性项\n",
        "\n",
        "函数`I()`将项包装起来"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "nteract": {
          "transient": {
            "deleting": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "lm.fit2=lm(medv~lstat+I(lstat^2),data = Boston)\n",
        "summary(lm.fit2)"
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "\n",
              "Call:\n",
              "lm(formula = medv ~ lstat + I(lstat^2), data = Boston)\n",
              "\n",
              "Residuals:\n",
              "     Min       1Q   Median       3Q      Max \n",
              "-15.2834  -3.8313  -0.5295   2.3095  25.4148 \n",
              "\n",
              "Coefficients:\n",
              "             Estimate Std. Error t value Pr(>|t|)    \n",
              "(Intercept) 42.862007   0.872084   49.15   <2e-16 ***\n",

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "用`contrasts()`函数以得到R生产的虚拟变量的具体情况"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "nteract": {
          "transient": {
            "deleting": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "contrasts(Carseats$ShelveLoc)"
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "display_data",
          "data": {
            "text/html": [
              "<table>\n",
              "<caption>A matrix: 3 × 2 of type dbl</caption>\n",
              "<thead>\n",
              "\t<tr><th></th><th scope=col>Good</th><th scope=col>Medium</th></tr>\n",
              "</thead>\n",
              "<tbody>\n",
              "\t<tr><th scope=row>Bad</th><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr>\n",
              "\t<tr><th scope=row>Good</th><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>\n",
              "\t<tr><th scope=row>Medium</th><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr>\n",
              "</tbody>\n",
              "</table>\n"
            ],
            "text/markdown": [
              "\n",
              "A matrix: 3 × 2 of type dbl\n",
              "\n",
              "| <!--/--> | Good | Medium |\n",
              "|---|---|---|\n",
              "| Bad | 0 | 0 |\n",
